> stalled out, later it gets cool and doesn't leak.
>
> another thing that was not heat sensitive but might have some
> affect. there are a lot of plugs and connectors, one of them looked fine
> on the outside, but one of the contacts came loose and was pushed back
> into the plug and wasn't making good contact.
